Frida

1. Overview
Use Cases:
- Bypassing Root/Jailbreak detection
- Runtime function hooking
- Dumping memory
- تحليل Android/iOS apps
- تجاوز SSL Pinning

---

2. Key Features
- Dynamic code injection
- JavaScript-based instrumentation
- Android, iOS, Windows, Linux, macOS support
- Hooking Java + Native code
- Powerful RE tools

---

3. Installation
Linux / macOS
pip install frida-tools


Android Device
bash
نسخ الكود
adb push frida-server /data/local/tmp/
adb shell "chmod 755 /data/local/tmp/frida-server"
adb shell "/data/local/tmp/frida-server &"

Windows

pip install frida-tools

---

4. Usage Examples
List running processes:
frida-ps -U
Inject script:

frida -U -f com.example.app -l script.js --no-pause
Example hook:

Java.perform(function () {
    var cls = Java.use("com.example.Class");
    cls.targetMethod.implementation = function () {
        console.log("Hooked!");
        return this.targetMethod();
    };
});

---

5. Important Commands
Command	Description
frida-ps	List processes
frida-trace	Auto-generate hooks
frida-server	Required for device instrumentation
-U	Attach to USB device

----

6. Advanced Use Cases
Bypassing SSL Pinning
Hooking native libraries (libc, libssl)
Reverse engineering protected Android apps
Extracting runtime secrets

